.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-BACKUP-VERIFY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-backup-verify \- verify integrity of a wallet backup file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-backup-verify
.I backup_path
.RI [ wallet ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens the SQLite file at
.I backup_path
and runs
.B PRAGMA integrity_check
to confirm the backup is a valid, uncorrupted database.
Returns
.B {"ok":true}
with the file size on success.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"size_bytes":N}
{"ok":false,"reason":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-backup (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1)
